{"tid":896790,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果Airpods2不但預計將會在12月推出市面   還跟Supreme推出聯乘系列？","createTime":"2018-11-10T10:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T14:09:38.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"027e89fd71f5732797e4832bfc9894feb087d078","tid":896790,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"今年蘋果一口氣推出新款iPhone XS，iPad Pro等產品，而 AirPods2 亦是焦點之一。據外國科技網站 Apple Insider 報道，新一代AirPods近日過了藍牙SIG（藍牙技術聯盟）的認證，預計將會在12月就推出市面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SpZ1CKz9euiV5gIzkR6BRQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/marie_claire_729/75c92ec7554ea77cdba0a9da13f4c7ff\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSpZ1CKz9euiV5gIzkR6BRQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fmarie_claire_729%2F75c92ec7554ea77cdba0a9da13f4c7ff&h=9a9125dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息指新款AirPods2雖然外形跟舊款沒有太大的改變，但將會採用藍牙 5.0 無線傳輸，接收範圍增至300公尺，而且亦新增防水和降噪功能，絕對是必入手的新耳機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/scr4MP46Urwb.vpVuoTNEA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/marie_claire_729/da6dd7bc37bafded624f9f1d61120384\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fscr4MP46Urwb.vpVuoTNEA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fmarie_claire_729%2Fda6dd7bc37bafded624f9f1d61120384&h=7310b366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20181024/720pix/1540393276_d7a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20181024%2F720pix%2F1540393276_d7a0.jpg&h=f04fd1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正當新一代Apple AirPods的消息傳得熱烘烘之際，網上亦流傳另一則帖文，由照片可見，Apple Airpods印上Supreme 著名的紅色 Box Logo，難道蘋果將會跟Supreme聯手推出Airpods系列？雖然消息未經證實，而很多粉絲亦留言表示消息不可信，但亦有網民表示「肯定是假的，但出了一定是要買的」，看來有了Supreme的加持，購買慾望又更強烈了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SaEazx7LADbF8DeggQOQKQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/marie_claire_729/43cdcd708d8967924a795151078ffded\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSaEazx7LADbF8DeggQOQKQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fmarie_claire_729%2F43cdcd708d8967924a795151078ffded&h=c428342e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d546bdd4d417c5236ccfa460f3350dc71f7f367","tid":896790,"uid":41245,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"集所有overpriced嘅嘢訴一身"},{"pid":"c414a774752ed0d6eadc45ddc3542b098a967b48","tid":896790,"uid":158977,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"新airpod關朱千雪咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2a59b3796ae07a9a04b42185c9cf9ac5ac16d6","tid":896790,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9692678314eeb376e7c51460fa8884902f344d","tid":896790,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"Supreme<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4fac89d9bd5e5fe80df01a60975f78ac44fade","tid":896790,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-